  "texts": [
    "This is a significant improvement over the base T5 model, which achieved a ROUGE-1 score of 8.01% on the test set.While the results are promising, there is still room for improvement.",
    "Future work could explore other fine-tuning methods or use additional datasets to further enhance the model's performance.",
    "This project lays a solid foundation for future research in the field of legal document summarization.",
    "It has the potential to significantly contribute to the efficiency and accessibility of legal proceedings, thereby having a profound impact on the legal system.KEYWORDS:Abstractive Summarization, Indian Legal Documents, T5 Transformer Model, Quantized Low-Rank Adaptation (QLoRA), Bert-Extractive-Summarizer, ROUGE-1 Score Copyright© 2024, IERJ.",
